00:26:21,127 --> 00:26:22,850
m'hot gebombet, dos iz gevezn

664
00:26:22,850 --> 00:26:24,127
ALEJE JEROZOLIMSKIEs

665
00:26:24,127 --> 00:26:24,850
un KRUCZA

666
00:26:24,850 --> 00:26:26,868
iz gev- ALEJE JEROZOLIMSKIE UNK der groyser

667
00:26:26,868 --> 00:26:28,442
ban STATION.

668
00:26:28,738 --> 00:26:33,572
un ikh bin geven di KRUCZA zibn. dos iz gevezn ALEJE JEROZOLIMSKIE mit di ALEJA MARSZALKOWSKA

669
00:26:33,572 --> 00:26:35,220
iz a ECKE, di CORNER

670
00:26:35,294 --> 00:26:37,238
un dort hot men undz genumen di khevre

671
00:26:37,313 --> 00:26:38,703
az me zol zayn

672
00:26:38,849 --> 00:26:41,330
d- fayer lesher. d- bombes, m'hot gevorfn

673
00:26:41,330 --> 00:26:42,867
bren bombes hobn zey gevorfn

674
00:26:42,867 --> 00:26:44,960
hobn mir geloshn di bombe mit zamd

675
00:26:45,293 --> 00:26:46,886
⟨in eynem⟩ in tsveytn hoyz

676
00:26:46,886 --> 00:26:49,182
s'iz adurkhgan oyf di MARSZALKOWSKA, iz arayn a bombe

677
00:26:49,182 --> 00:26:50,256
zi hot nisht oyfgerisn.

678
00:26:50,349 --> 00:26:52,867
azoy iz men dort gevezn biz di ende

679
00:26:52,997 --> 00:26:53,793
di milkhome

680
00:26:53,812 --> 00:26:54,886
hot men zikh untergegebn.

681
00:26:55,478 --> 00:26:58,627
der UNK untergegebn, hot men gezogt me ken shoyn aheymgeyn keyn Lodzh

682
00:26:58,867 --> 00:27:00,478
hot men ongehoybn tsu geyn.

683
00:27:00,848 --> 00:27:03,551
tsu fus. m'iz tsugekumen, zenen mir geganen nokh Blonye.

684
00:27:04,051 --> 00:27:06,533
oyfn veg hot men undz gekhapt do, di yekes

685
00:27:06,829 --> 00:27:09,570
un hobn gezogt m'iz militer, un m'hot undz arayngefirt

686
00:27:09,570 --> 00:27:11,774
der fabrik UNK Blonye

687
00:27:11,774 --> 00:27:14,181
dort, dort zenen mir gelign efsher a por tog

688
00:27:14,181 --> 00:27:15,792
dort iz gelign fil militer

689
00:27:16,477 --> 00:27:20,977
un azoy zenen mir dort gelign, hobn zey undz genumen d- fun dortn. m'hot undz gefirt keyn GORLITZ

690
00:27:21,200 --> 00:27:24,200
dos heyst GORLITZ, STALAG akht A.

691
00:27:24,349 --> 00:27:26,182
dort bin ikh gekumen keyn GORLITZ.

692
00:27:26,478 --> 00:27:28,830
azoy bin ikh gekumen keyn GORLITZ

693
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:30,941
hobn zey gezukht dort SANITATOR.

694
00:27:31,182 --> 00:27:32,515
ikh bin nokh gevezn

695
00:27:32,515 --> 00:27:34,645
do hot zikh gezogt, bin a SANITATOR

696
00:27:35,163 --> 00:27:36,775
hot men mikh genumen ⟨a⟩ SANITATOR

697
00:27:36,775 --> 00:27:39,126
hot men mikh araynge⟨UNK⟩, un dort iz gevezn

698
00:27:39,126 --> 00:27:41,941
ikh hob im nisht gevust ver dos, iz gevezn der shrayber.

699
00:27:41,996 --> 00:27:44,200
er iz gefaln in gefangenish, iz gevezn

700
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:45,422
a poylisher

701
00:27:45,422 --> 00:27:47,274
minister, heyst ZAWADZKI.

702
00:27:48,144 --> 00:27:49,311
er iz gevezn

703
00:27:49,311 --> 00:27:51,811
GENERAL BORTNOWSKI's

704
00:27:51,811 --> 00:27:54,292
GENERAL BORTNOWSKI's anderer man

705
00:27:54,292 --> 00:27:56,348
un er iz dort geven der shrayber

706
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,163
hot mikh ge- bin ikh gevorn

707
00:27:59,163 --> 00:28:01,810
a SANITATOR, gekrign a paske, un gegagnen, g- dos

708
00:28:01,810 --> 00:28:03,607
s'hot gedoyert umgefer akht

709
00:28:03,607 --> 00:28:05,125
tog oder tsvey vokhn

710
00:28:05,292 --> 00:28:06,810
iz gevezn an opruf

711
00:28:06,810 --> 00:28:08,199
bakant makhung

712
00:28:08,199 --> 00:28:09,051
ale

713
00:28:09,051 --> 00:28:12,125
yidn vos iz do muzn zikh tsushteln

714
00:28:12,496 --> 00:28:13,866
ts- anisht iz toyt shtrof.

715
00:28:14,199 --> 00:28:16,181
hobn dokh di yidn tsugeshtelt.

716
00:28:16,421 --> 00:28:18,477
bin ikh gegangen arayn tsu dem ZAWADZKI

717
00:28:18,477 --> 00:28:19,588
geven der shrayber

718
00:28:19,625 --> 00:28:22,921
un gefregt im "vos zol ikh tun?" zogt er "ikh ken dir nisht helfn.

719
00:28:23,031 --> 00:28:23,865
gey aroyf

720
00:28:24,476 --> 00:28:26,865
tsum OBERLE- UNK ⟨firme⟩

721
00:28:26,865 --> 00:28:30,161
er vet dir zogn yo oder nisht." bin ikh aroyfgeganen tsum o- UNK

722
00:28:30,161 --> 00:28:31,050
UNK

723
00:28:31,606 --> 00:28:33,457
kent a i- a bisl daytsh?

724
00:28:33,457 --> 00:28:38,050
ikh geb a shtel oyf mikh un tsugeklapt mit di fis. ikh meld zikh UNK

725
00:28:38,050 --> 00:28:39,754
zogt er tsu mir "du kenst blaybn."

726
00:28:40,309 --> 00:28:41,864
bin ikh aruntergan un geblibn

727
00:28:41,864 --> 00:28:44,716
un di ale yidn hot men nebekh genumen. m'hot zey avekgeshikt

728
00:28:44,957 --> 00:28:48,383
un mer hot nisht gevust fun gornisht. mir hobn nisht keyn UNK keyn shum anung.

